    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is in good condition and has been consistently well-maintained, making it an excellent choice for anyone seeking a reliable and attractive daily driver. The engine performs smoothly, and the transmission shifts with precision, reflecting its careful upkeep over the years. While there are some minor signs of normal use, the exterior and interior have been kept clean and are in great shape overall. You can expect a comfortable and dependable driving experience from this solid, road-ready car.",
      "price": 33500.0,
      "reputation": 1.0,
      "quality": "good",
      "quality_value": 0.7,
      "timestep_posted": 34
    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_2_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_2",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and serves as a reliable daily driver, though it shows clear signs of its age and mileage. The exterior has several noticeable dings, some paint fading on the hood, and a few scuffs on the rear bumper. Inside, the upholstery is intact but shows some staining and wear on the driver's seat. Mechanically, the car runs and drives, but it will likely need suspension work and a new set of tires in the near future. It\u2019s a solid choice for someone looking for an affordable entry-point vehicle who doesn't mind a bit of cosmetic character.",
      "price": 19500.0,
      "reputation": 1.0,
      "quality": "fair",
      "quality_value": 0.4,
      "timestep_posted": 34
    },
    {
      "id": "standard_1_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "standard_1",
      "description": "This vehicle is in poor condition. The exterior has significant damage, including deep scratches, dents, and fading paint. The interior shows heavy wear and tear, with torn upholstery and broken components. Mechanically, the car requires substantial repairs to be fully operational.",
      "price": 4500.0,
      "reputation": 1.0,
      "quality": "poor",
